          "text": "The nth term is a\u2099 = n(n + 1).  \n\u2013 The 10th term is a\u2081\u2080 = 10\u00b711 = 110.  \n\u2013 The sum of the first 10 terms is  \n  \u2211\u2099\u208c\u2081\u00b9\u2070 n(n + 1) = \u2211(n\u00b2 + n)  \n                  = (10\u00b711\u00b721)/6 + (10\u00b711)/2  \n                  = 385 + 55  \n                  = 440.  \nOr, using the closed\u2010form for the sum of pronic numbers,  \n  \u2211\u2099\u208c\u2081\u1d3a n(n + 1) = N(N + 1)(N + 2)/3,  \nso for N=10: 10\u00b711\u00b712/3 = 440."
        }
